# Coverage exclusions (covr reads this gitignore-style).
#
# R/zzz.R is the package .onLoad hook: it registers S3 methods into the
# nlmixr2est / knitr namespaces at load time. That code runs during package
# loading, before covr attaches its instrumentation, so covr structurally
# cannot record it as covered (it reports ~5%). Excluding it makes the
# reported percentage reflect code that is actually measurable by tests.
R/zzz.R
